EDA

To mimic their project I guess they use tree-based models to predict wether or not a Pokemon is legendary.

It seems they got legendary happy in the 7-generation of Pokemon… Not sure what games those are since I haven’t played since Pokemon Red.

recipe(volcano_type ~ ., data = volcano_df) %>% update_role(volcano_number, new_role = “Id”) %>% step_other(tectonic_settings) %>% step_other(major_rock_1) %>% step_dummy(tectonic_settings, major_rock_1) %>% step_zv(all_predictors()) %>% step_normalize(all_predictors()) %>% step_smote(volcano_type)
